dct_title_s: Major military installations / MillitaryTimes Media Group.
dct_description_sm: At head of title: ArmyTimes, Air ForceTimes and Corps MarineTimes. On verso: "Supplement to Army Times, Air Force Times and Marine Corps Times." Map shows major military installations in the United states. Includes ancillary maps of "San Diego Area," "Hawaiin Islands," "Oahu," "Alaska," "Washington D.C. area," and "Gulf coast area and chart of "Overseas permanent installations." Ancillary maps:"San Diego Area," "Hawaiin Islands," "Oahu," "Alaska," "Washington D.C. area," and "Gulf coast area." Listing of "Overseas permanent installations." Includes names and websites for Military Times Media Group newspapers and other advertisements.
